    Tag Usage
  </bolt-text>
  <bolt-text>
    <bolt-code-snippet display="inline" lang="html">&lt;bolt-text&gt;</bolt-code-snippet> allows for separation of semantics and visual. Using a semantically correct tag will not affect the appearance of the text.
  </bolt-text>
  {% for tag in schema.properties.tag.enum %}

